# This outer directory is a LOCAL workspace repository.
#
# `gstack/` is a SEPARATE third-party git repository
# (https://github.com/garrytan/gstack.git) with its own history. Keep it out of
# this repo so it is never staged or committed here, and so `git add` at the root
# can never turn it into a broken embedded-repo gitlink. Manage gstack from inside
# `gstack/` with its own git.
gstack/

